--- a/CHANGELOG.md
+++ b/CHANGELOG.md
@@ -25,6 +25,7 @@ This project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/).
 
 ### Changed
 
+* **BREAKING**: The default code style is changed from `intellij_idea` to `ktlint_official`. The `ktlint_official` code style adheres to the best parts of the [Kotlin Coding Conventions](https://kotlinlang.org/docs/coding-conventions.html) and [Android Kotlin style guide](https://developer.android.com/kotlin/style-guide). It is no longer restricted to produce code that is compatible with the default IntelliJ IDEA formatter which has bugs that have not been resolved after multiple years. If you want to continue using the `intellij_idea` code style, set `.editorconfig` property `ktlint_code_style=intellij_idea` explicitly.
 * Update dependency gradle to v8.2.1 ([#2122](https://github.com/pinterest/ktlint/pull/2122))
 * Update dependency org.codehaus.janino:janino to v3.1.10  ([#2110](https://github.com/pinterest/ktlint/pull/2110))
 * Update dependency com.google.jimfs:jimfs to v1.3.0 ([#2112](https://github.com/pinterest/ktlint/pull/2112))
